      "span_text": "These controversial data on characteristics of SS associated with SSc are probably due to the lack of a consensual definition of sSS until recently. sSS is now clearly defined by criteria from the American-European consensus group (AECG) published in 2002  and thus, the characteristics of patients with SS and SSc can now be studied."
